    <p>I started out this project by corralling the key stakeholders to discuss goals of the site, priorities that each subgroup of the Rec Sports, and possible directions. We also created key personas (following my <a href="">design process</a>) at that initial meeting so that the proposed design and content would stay focused. As our design meetings continued, I also tested my plans with real users to validate them.</p>

